events.name: Western Kentucky Hilltoppers at Old Dominion Monarchs

headlines.description: Mike White threw five touchdown passes for the second straight game and Western Kentucky scored 14 straight points in the fourth quarter to rally past Old Dominion 35-31 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: White throws for 5 TDs again, WKU rallies past ODU 35-31

events.name: Marshall Thundering Herd at Middle Tennessee Blue Raiders

headlines.description: Tyler King and Keion Davis each scored two rushing touchdowns to help Marshall beat Middle Tennessee 38-10 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Marshall runs for 4 TDs in 38-10 win over Middle Tennessee

events.name: Air Force Falcons at Nevada Wolf Pack

headlines.description: Timothy McVey led three Air Force rushers with 100-plus yards and Luke Strebel kicked a 30-yard field goal as time expired to help Air Force beat Nevada 45-42 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Strebel kicks game-winner, Air Force runs past Nevada 45-42

events.name: Colorado State Rams at New Mexico Lobos

headlines.description: Nick Stevens threw for two touchdowns in Colorado State's 21-point second quarter and the Rams defense forced a fourth-quarter turnover in a 27-24 victory over New Mexico on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Stevens' 2 TDs lead Colorado State past New Mexico 27-24

video.headline: Johnson wins jump ball in end zone for Colorado State TD
